Text: 'Presidential Proclamation-Civil War Sesquicentennial'
k: publisher
Text: 'The White House'
k: date
Text: 'April 12, 2011'
k: quote
Text: '...a new meaning was conferred on our country's name...'
k: archiveurl
Text: 'http://www.webcitation.org/62aAPoA6B'
